question: Which countries in Europe have at least 3 car manufacturers?

JOIN car_names cn ON cm.Id = cn.MakeId

WHERE ct.Continent = 'europe'
GROUP BY c.CountryName
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT cm.Id) >= 3
